sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as CreateToolWizard<br/>useToolWizardForm
    participant API as AugmentApi<br/>toolEndpoints.ts
    participant BE as augment-backend<br/>kagentiToolRoutes
    participant KG as Kagenti Operator<br/>API
    participant K8s as Kubernetes
    participant SW as Shipwright<br/>Build System

    rect rgb(224, 231, 255)
        Note over User,UI: Step 1 - Basics
        User->>UI: Enter name, namespace, protocol, framework
        UI->>UI: DNS-1123 validation
        UI->>UI: Check name warning (e.g. -mcp suffix)
        User->>UI: Click Next
    end

    rect rgb(219, 234, 254)
        Note over User,UI: Step 2 - Deployment
        alt Image Deploy
            User->>UI: Select "Container Image"
            User->>UI: Enter image URL, pull secret
        else Source Deploy
            User->>UI: Select "Git Source"
            User->>UI: Enter git URL, revision, context dir
            User->>UI: Configure registry, build strategy, Dockerfile
        end
        User->>UI: Click Next
    end

    rect rgb(237, 233, 254)
        Note over User,UI: Step 3 - Runtime
        User->>UI: Select workload type (Deployment/StatefulSet)
        User->>UI: Configure env vars, service ports
        User->>UI: Toggle HTTP route, auth bridge, SPIRE
        User->>UI: Click Create / Build
    end

    rect rgb(209, 250, 229)
        Note over UI,K8s: Submit - Image Deploy Path
        UI->>UI: buildToolRequest(formState)
        UI->>API: createKagentiTool(body)
        API->>BE: POST /kagenti/tools
        BE->>BE: Validate name + namespace
        BE->>KG: POST /api/v1/tools
        KG->>K8s: Create Tool CRD
        K8s->>K8s: Deployment + Service + Route
        KG-->>BE: { success, name, namespace }
        BE-->>API: 200 OK
        API-->>UI: Success
        UI->>User: Show success snackbar
    end

    rect rgb(207, 250, 254)
        Note over UI,SW: Submit - Source Deploy Path
        UI->>API: createKagentiTool(body)
        API->>BE: POST /kagenti/tools
        BE->>KG: POST /api/v1/tools
        KG->>K8s: Create Build CRD
        KG-->>BE: { success }
        BE-->>UI: Success

        Note over UI,SW: Step 4 - Build Polling
        loop Every 5 seconds
            UI->>API: getToolBuildInfo(ns, name)
            API->>BE: GET /kagenti/tools/:ns/:name/build-info
            BE->>KG: GET /api/v1/tools/:ns/:name/build-info
            KG->>SW: Check BuildRun status
            SW-->>KG: { phase, startTime, completionTime }
            KG-->>BE: Build status
            BE-->>UI: Build status
        end

        SW->>SW: Clone + Build + Push image
        UI->>UI: Build completes

        UI->>API: finalizeToolBuild(ns, name, body)
        API->>BE: POST /kagenti/tools/:ns/:name/finalize-build
        BE->>KG: POST /api/v1/tools/:ns/:name/finalize-build
        KG->>K8s: Create Deployment from built image
        K8s->>K8s: Deployment + Service + Route
        KG-->>BE: { success }
        BE-->>UI: Success
        UI->>User: Show success + close wizard
    end
